Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
unplaceJtag(25.10)                                          unplaceJtag(25.10)

Name
       unplaceJtag  -  Changes the placement status of JTAG inst from FIXED to
       PLACED

Syntax
       unplaceJtag

       Changes the placement status of JTAG inst from FIXED  to  PLACED.  This
       command can be used after the placeJtag command.

Parameters
       None

Examples
       The  following  set of commands places all Jtag instances of cell INVX1
       as FIXED, and then using unplaceJtag to change their status to PLACED:

       specifyJtag -cell INVX1

       placeJtag

       unplaceJtag

